 store and keep customers coming back for more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/4b4c7cf3d1c6501208cde7a410261017.poster.avif?t=1738001809\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/4b4c7cf3d1c6501208cde7a410261017.webm?t=1738001809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/4b4c7cf3d1c6501208cde7a410261017.mp4?t=1738001809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cleaning Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maintain cleanliness in your store with the cleaning gameplay feature. Sweep floors, wipe down walls from graffiti, and take out the trash to ensure a pleasant shopping environment. Cleanliness affects customer satisfaction and store reputation, adding another layer of realism and management to the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/2555a210e0356d0d61e5425ce131dba3.poster.avif?t=1738001809\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/2555a210e0356d0d61e5425ce131dba3.webm?t=1738001809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/2555a210e0356d0d61e5425ce131dba3.mp4?t=1738001809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mini-Games</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have fun with extra mini-games, including a basketball mini-game where you can take a break and shoot some hoops. Look forward to more mini-games we plan on adding in future updates to provide variety and additional entertainment within the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/1aea716e2d9e5903c48cadca7be90c99.poster.avif?t=1738001809\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/1aea716e2d9e5903c48cadca7be90c99.webm?t=1738001809\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2282410/extras/1aea716e2d9e5903c48cadca7be90c99.mp4?t=1738001809\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join Us on Discord: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
